    "# Fashion-MNIST CNN experiments\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook explores several simple neural-network architectures on the Fashion-MNIST dataset.\n",
    "We train and compare:\n",
    "- small convolutional models (different capacities),\n",
    "- MLP baseline,\n",
    "- variants with Batch Normalization and Dropout.\n",
    "\n",
    "The goals are:\n",
    "1. Learn the shape and preprocessing required for Keras convolutional models.\n",
    "2. Compare accuracy and generalization across architectures.\n",
    "3. Visualize training curves and a few predictions.\n",
    "\n",
    "Dependencies: Python 3.8+, `tensorflow` (or `tensorflow>=2.x`), `keras` (bundled with tf), `numpy`, `matplotlib`."
   ]
  },
